 235:Src/system_stm32n6xx_s.c ****   *             multiplied/divided by the PLL factors.
 236:Src/system_stm32n6xx_s.c ****   *
 237:Src/system_stm32n6xx_s.c ****   *         (*) HSI_VALUE default value is 64 MHz.
 238:Src/system_stm32n6xx_s.c ****   *             With the HAL, HSI_VALUE is a constant defined in stm32n6xx_hal_conf.h file
